title: Who Runs The World? INSECTS! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 75
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The BABES are back from Coachella and ready to gossip. They talk insects! Whats your fav bug? Chris' baby does something CRAZY! Ants are so talented. OLD AS F is the hottest charity in the streetz babe. Shout out Lizzo we love her! Could you fight an animal that was attacking you?! Chris and Sal imagine fighting everything from a hawk to an army of 5th graders. WORST FLIGHT IN HISTORY. The government now has LASER BEAMS. Eagles are WILD. What do pet snakes eat? How is snake food made? Shout out Sergio Chicon! MOST INSANE BUGS!!! People sleeping on the highway in their self driving car.....THE FUTURE IS SUS AS F BABES.
